teaser:
A great machine shop in the Twin Cities, MN is looking for a experienced CNC Machinist. The company does prototyping for medical, and aerospace. A good candidate for this position will have 2+ years of experience as a CNC machinist in vertical/horiztontal mills, lathes, or swiss. Candidate should demonstrate a strong stable work history. Need to be able to do own programming and set up. The company is looking for someone who wants to grow with the company and is looking for a career. The company offers competitive benefits, 401k, and vacation.

If you have any questions about the position please call April at 651-633-4080 or email april.brausen@randstadusa.com

Working hours: All shifts

Requirements:
*Able to pass a background and drug screen
*Degree in CNC machining
*2+ years of experience
*Stong, Stable Work History
*Master Cam and/or Surf Cam experience prefered but not necessary

Randstad is a world leader in matching great people with great companies.
